Available Tools: create_folder | move_file | copy_file | rename_file | delete_file | list_folder
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "path": "string", "destination": "string", "new_name": "string" }
Response Schema: { "path": "string", "entries": [{ "name": "string", "type": "file|folder", "size_bytes": number }], "status": "string" }
---
Question: Create a new folder named "Q4_Reports" inside the projects directory.
Call: { "func_call": "create_folder", "path": "/projects/Q4_Reports", "destination": "", "new_name": "" }
Response: { "path": "/projects", "entries": [{ "name": "Q4_Reports", "type": "folder", "size_bytes": 0 }, { "name": "budget.xlsx", "type": "file", "size_bytes": 24500 }], "status": "success" }

